data.value: We hereby entrust to you the following goods for Manufacturing / Inspection on approval basis with the following condition. 1. The Goods remain our property. 2. You will not sell or pledge or mortgage the said goods or otherwise deal with them in any manner which is prejudicial to our right. 3. The goods willl be returned to us forthwith on demand. 4. The good will be held while in your custody at your risk in all respects. 5. You will be responsible for the said goods in the same condition in which it was given to you or polished goods if it was given for Manufacturing. 6. The diamonds herein on memo are exclusively of natural origin and untreated based on personal knowledge and / or written guarantee provided by supplier of these daimonds. 7. The acceptance of goods herein on memo will be as per the WFDB guidelines. 8. Subject to Mumbai Jurisdiction.
